<div class="layout-row flex">
  <div class="flex template layout-column">
    <div class="flex flex-gt-xs-33">
      {{#paper-card class="blog-title-card" as |card|}}
          <h1>Blog Name</h1>
        {{/paper-card}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="layout-row layout-xs-column">
    <div class="flex flex-gt-xs-80">
        {{#paper-card class="bio-container" as |card|}}
          {{#card.title as |title|}}
            <p>Church-key ethical succulents, YOLO affogato next level letterpress
                8-bit lo-fi ugh jean shorts tousled kickstarter microdosing
                polaroid. Narwhal hell of butcher cray, woke kickstarter dreamcatcher
                 mlkshk letterpress celiac tofu edison bulb gastropub church-key
                  distillery.</p>
          {{/card.title}}
          {{#card.actions class="layout-row layout-align-start-center" as |actions|}}
         {{#actions.icons}}
           <!-- {{#paper-button iconButton=true}}{{paper-icon 'favorite'}}{{/paper-button}} -->
           <img src="assets/facebook.png" alt="" class="social-icon">
           <img src="assets/twitter.png" alt="" class="social-icon">
           <img src="assets/instagram.png" alt="" class="social-icon">
         {{/actions.icons}}
       {{/card.actions}}
        {{/paper-card}}
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-gt-xs-20">
        {{#paper-card as |card|}}
            {{card.image size="md" src="https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/759389830975455232/4-UdzhN5_400x400.jpg" alt="Tomster" title="Johnny"}}
        {{/paper-card}}
    </div>
</div>
<div class="layout-row layout-xs-column blog-container">
  <div class=" flex blog-content">
    {{#paper-card as |card|}}
        {{#card.title as |title|}}
          {{#title.text as |text|}}
            {{#text.headline}}Blog Post Title{{/text.headline}}
            {{#text.subhead}}Blog Post Sub-Title{{/text.subhead}}
          {{/title.text}}
        {{/card.title}}
        {{#card.content class="layout-row layout-align-space-between"}}
        <p>Migas air plant 8-bit, salvia YOLO distillery polaroid typewriter blue bottle mustache vaporware. Pabst cronut small batch gluten-free vegan, drinking vinegar chillwave before they sold out yuccie cray. Poke cliche green juice polaroid cardigan kitsch. PBR&B meditation wolf hashtag asymmetrical. Everyday carry farm-to-table jean shorts, knausgaard tbh readymade mlkshk. Chambray kogi master cleanse, la croix fixie crucifix semiotics woke. Pork belly swag thundercats, intelligentsia occupy bitters scenester. Fashion axe mustache vegan prism. Meggings activated charcoal copper mug roof party. Man braid occupy ethical health goth, tbh shabby chic la croix organic YOLO brooklyn banh mi slow-carb. Lyft marfa tbh coloring book you probably haven't heard of them. Viral pabst paleo, fanny pack ennui tousled taxidermy meggings banh mi. Master cleanse pork belly trust fund four loko leggings marfa. Hella wayfarers pinterest freegan pork belly, keffiyeh air plant seitan lyft biodiesel blue bottle normcore drinking vinegar pabst.</p>
          {{#card.media size="xl"}}
            <div class="card-media"></div>
          {{/card.media}}
          {{#card.actions class="layout-column"}}
            {{#paper-button iconButton=true}}{{paper-icon "favorite"}}{{/paper-button}}
            {{#paper-button iconButton=true}}{{paper-icon "settings"}}{{/paper-button}}
            {{#paper-button iconButton=true}}{{paper-icon "share"}}{{/paper-button}}
          {{/card.actions}}
        {{/card.content}}
      {{/paper-card}}
  </div>
</div>
